fields.name: AD
fields.description: Allelic depths for the ref and alt alleles in the order listed

fields.name: DP
fields.description: Approximate read depth (reads with MQ=255 or with bad mates are filtered)

fields.name: GQ
fields.description: Genotype Quality

fields.name: GT
fields.description: Genotype

fields.name: MIN_DP
fields.description: Minimum DP observed within the GVCF block

fields.name: PL
fields.description: Normalized, Phred-scaled likelihoods for genotypes as defined in the VCF specification

fields.name: SB
fields.description: Per-sample component statistics which comprise the Fisher's Exact Test to detect strand bias.

fields.name: AC
fields.description: Allele count in genotypes, for each ALT allele, in the same order as listed

fields.name: AF
fields.description: Allele Frequency, for each ALT allele, in the same order as listed

fields.name: AN
fields.description: Total number of alleles in called genotypes

fields.name: BaseQRankSum
fields.description: Z-score from Wilcoxon rank sum test of Alt Vs. Ref base qualities

fields.name: CCC
fields.description: Number of called chromosomes

fields.name: ClippingRankSum
fields.description: Z-score From Wilcoxon rank sum test of Alt vs. Ref number of hard clipped bases

fields.name: DP
fields.description: Approximate read depth; some reads may have been filtered

fields.name: DS
fields.description: Were any of the samples downsampled?

fields.name: END
fields.description: Stop position of the interval

fields.name: FS
fields.description: Phred-scaled p-value using Fisher's exact test to detect strand bias

fields.name: GQ_MEAN
fields.description: Mean of all GQ values

fields.name: GQ_STDDEV
fields.description: Standard deviation of all GQ values

fields.name: HWP
fields.description: P value from test of Hardy Weinberg Equilibrium

fields.name: HaplotypeScore
fields.description: Consistency of the site with at most two segregating haplotypes

fields.name: InbreedingCoeff
fields.description: Inbreeding coefficient as estimated from the genotype likelihoods per-sample when compared against the Hardy-Weinberg expectation

fields.name: MLEAC
fields.description: Maximum likelihood expectation (MLE) for the allele counts (not necessarily the same as the AC), for each ALT allele, in the same order as listed

fields.name: MLEAF
fields.description: Maximum likelihood expectation (MLE) for the allele frequency (not necessarily the same as the AF), for each ALT allele, in the same order as listed

fields.name: MQ
fields.description: RMS Mapping Quality

fields.name: MQ0
fields.description: Total Mapping Quality Zero Reads

fields.name: MQRankSum
fields.description: Z-score From Wilcoxon rank sum test of Alt vs. Ref read mapping qualities

fields.name: NCC
fields.description: Number of no-called samples

fields.name: QD
fields.description: Variant Confidence/Quality by Depth

fields.name: ReadPosRankSum
fields.description: Z-score from Wilcoxon rank sum test of Alt vs. Ref read position bias

fields.name: SOR
fields.description: Symmetric Odds Ratio of 2x2 contingency table to detect strand bias
